# EXECUTIA Governance Rules

- EXECUTIA is an execution-time truth system.
- Never treat legacy projections as canonical truth.
- Canonical truth:
  - ledger_entries = material truth
  - supplemental audit chain = canonical audit proof
- Verification endpoints must be read-only.
- Never mutate audit chain rows.
- Never expose service role keys or internal keys in frontend code.
- No black backgrounds in UI.
- Use light institutional interface design.
